(i)  The design pattern used was: Design by proxy: by not editing the original data at once and reupdating the database at the same time we reduce the risk of false information being recorded.
(ii) The location of the test classes: CS3354-Double-Chocolate-Chip-Frappuccino\Calendar\app\src\test\java\com\example\calendar
(iii)Instructions to build the app: There are no special instructions required to launch our app
